<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="חבילת חתונה מושלמת - DJ + הגברה + תאורה ב-8,500 ש״ח בלבד">
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon_shmurata.png">

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Heebo:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('/images/lights.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .deal-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B00, #FF8C00);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,107,0,0.5); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,107,0,0.8); }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(36px, 8vw, 72px);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: #FF6B00;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 28px);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
        }

        .price-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,107,0,0.2), rgba(255,140,0,0.1));
            border: 3px solid #FF6B00;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px 50px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .price-old {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            text-decoration: line-through;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .price-new {
            font-size: clamp(48px, 10vw, 80px);
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #FF6B00;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,107,0,0.5);
        }

        .price-new span {
            font-size: 0.5em;
            color: white;
        }

        .includes-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .include-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .include-item i {
            color: #FF6B00;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        /* Benefits Section */
        .benefits {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section-title span {
            color: #FF6B00;
        }

        .benefits-text {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .benefits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .benefit-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,107,0,0.1), rgba(255,255,255,0.05));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .benefit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: #FF6B00;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255,107,0,0.2);
        }

        .benefit-card i {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #FF6B00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .benefit-card h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .benefit-card p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Gallery Section */
        .gallery {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: #0a0a0a;
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 16/10;
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,107,0,0.2), rgba(0,0,0,0.9));
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B00, #FF8C00);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255,107,0,0.4);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255,107,0,0.6);
        }

        .btn-whatsapp {
            background: #25D366;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37,211,102,0.4);
        }

        .btn-whatsapp:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(37,211,102,0.6);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid #FF6B00;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #FF6B00;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .contact-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .contact-name strong {
            color: #FF6B00;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .land-footer {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #000;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        }

        /* Animations */
        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

        /* Lightbox Styles */
        .lightbox {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            z-index: 9999;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .lightbox.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        .lightbox-content {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 90%;
            max-height: 85vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .lightbox-content img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 85vh;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .lightbox-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 30px;
            font-size: 40px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 10001;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .lightbox-close:hover {
            color: #FF6B00;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .lightbox-nav {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 50px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 10001;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .lightbox-nav:hover {
            color: #FF6B00;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }

        .lightbox-prev {
            left: 20px;
        }

        .lightbox-next {
            right: 20px;
        }

        .lightbox-counter {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .gallery-item::after {
            content: '\f00e';
            font-family: 'Font Awesome 6 Free';
            font-weight: 900;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
            font-size: 40px;
            color: white;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }

        .gallery-item:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        }

        /* Floating Buttons */
        .floating-whatsapp {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 9998;
        }

        .floating-whatsapp a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: #25D366;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .floating-whatsapp a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.7);
        }

        .floating-whatsapp i {
            color: white;
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        .floating-accessibility {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 9998;
        }

        .floating-accessibility button {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B00, #FF8C00);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .floating-accessibility button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.7);
        }

        .floating-accessibility i {
            color: white;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .accessibility-panel {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 70px;
            left: 0;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 260px;
            display: none;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
        }

        .accessibility-panel.active {
            display: block;
            animation: slideUp 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .accessibility-panel h3 {
            color: #FF6B00;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
        }

        .acc-option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .acc-option:hover {
            background: rgba(255,107,0,0.2);
        }

        .acc-option.active {
            background: rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
            border: 1px solid #FF6B00;
        }

        .acc-option span {
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .acc-option i {
            color: #FF6B00;
            font-size: 16px;
            width: 25px;
        }

        .acc-reset {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #FF6B00;
            color: #FF6B00;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .acc-reset:hover {
            background: #FF6B00;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Accessibility Styles */
        body.acc-bigger-text { font-size: 120% !important; }
        body.acc-bigger-text * { font-size: inherit !important; }
        body.acc-high-contrast { filter: contrast(1.5) !important; }
        body.acc-grayscale { filter: grayscale(1) !important; }
        body.acc-light-bg { background: #fff !important; }
        body.acc-light-bg * { background: #fff !important; color: #000 !important; }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                background-attachment: scroll;
            }

            .price-box {
                padding: 20px 30px;
            }

            .includes-list {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .include-item {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 350px;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .lightbox-nav {
                font-size: 30px;
                width: 45px;
                height: 45px;
            }

            .lightbox-prev {
                left: 10px;
            }

            .lightbox-next {
                right: 10px;
            }

            .gallery-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .gallery-item {
                aspect-ratio: 1/1;
            }
        }

        /* Logo Header Section */
        .logo-header {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg,
                rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.15) 0%,
                rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.08) 50%,
                transparent 100%);
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .logo-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 150%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center top,
                rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2) 0%,
                transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .logo-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.08) 0%, transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0%, transparent 40%);
            animation: floatGlow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        @keyframes floatGlow {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: translate(2%, 1%) rotate(1deg); }
            50% { transform: translate(0, 2%) rotate(0deg); }
            75% { transform: translate(-2%, 1%) rotate(-1deg); }
        }

        .logo-header img {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 280px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4))
                    drop-shadow(0 0 60px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2));
            animation: logoPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes logoPulse {
            0%, 100% {
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4))
                        drop-shadow(0 0 60px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2));
            }
            50% {
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.6))
                        drop-shadow(0 0 80px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3));
            }
        }

        .logo-header .glow-line {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg,
                transparent 0%,
                rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.8) 50%,
                transparent 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.5);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .logo-header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            .logo-header img {
                max-width: 200px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Logo Header -->
    <header class="logo-header">
        <img src="/images/big_logo-smurata.png" alt="שמורתא">
        <div class="glow-line"></div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="deal-badge fade-in">
                <i class="fas fa-fire"></i> מבצע מיוחד למתחתנים!
            </div>

            <h1 class="fade-in delay-1">
                חבילת חתונה <span>מושלמת</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in delay-2">
                DJ מטורף + הגברה איכותית + תאורה מרהיבה
            </p>

            <div class="price-box fade-in delay-3">
                <div class="price-old">במקום 12,000 ש"ח</div>
                <div class="price-new">8,500<span> ש"ח</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="includes-list fade-in delay-4">
                <div class="include-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-headphones-alt"></i>
                    <span>DJ מטורף</span>
                </div>
                <div class="include-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-volume-up"></i>
                    <span>מערכת הגברה</span>
                </div>
                <div class="include-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    <span>תאורת אווירה</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits Section -->
    <section class="benefits">
        <h2 class="section-title">למה <span>חבילה משולבת</span> משתלמת?</h2>

        <p class="benefits-text">
            כשאתם מזמינים DJ, הגברה ותאורה מספק אחד - אתם חוסכים כסף, זמן וכאב ראש.
            במקום לתאם בין 3 ספקים שונים, יש לכם איש קשר אחד שאחראי על הכל.
            DJ שמכיר את הציוד, יודע את מגבלות המערכות ומתנהל קל עם הצוות - ללא תקלות.
            התוצאה? אירוע חלק, מקצועי ובלי הפתעות.
        </p>

        <div class="benefits-grid">
            <div class="benefit-card">
                <i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"></i>
                <h3>חיסכון משמעותי</h3>
                <p>במקום לשלם ל-2 ספקים נפרדים (DJ כ-7,500 ש"ח, הגברה ותאורה כ-6,000 ש"ח) - אתם מקבלים הכל במחיר מוסכם מראש בהנחת דיל משמעותית!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-card">
                <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i>
                <h3>סנכרון מושלם</h3>
                <p>התאורה מסונכרנת למוזיקה, ההגברה מכוילת בדיוק כמו שצריך - הכל עובד יחד בהרמוניה מושלמת.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-card">
                <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>
                <h3>איש קשר אחד</h3>
                <p>במקום לרוץ בין ספקים, יש לכם נציג אחד שאחראי על הכל. פחות סטרס, יותר שקט נפשי.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-card">
